----> Add Power
## chmod o+w /root/
## chmod o+r /root/ 

----> Remove power
## chmod o-r /root/
## chmod o-w /root/

000  -- none
001  -- execute only
010  -- write only
100  -- read only
101  -- read and execute 
110  -- read and write 
111  -- read write exexcute


